### Description of Issue/Question

Ubuntu Xenial uses a new version of ifenslave, which does not know parameter use_carrier for bonding. It broke down connection to server and system error is:

`bonding: on invalid for parameter use_carrier`

This parameter can be removed in future version of ubuntu. 
### Setup

Setup simple Ubuntu Xenial with salt creation of network bonding active-backup. 
